{"tid":1638034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有行動 文宣post 轉曬去活動台","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T16:00:52.000Z","uid":150267,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77191d492e37f22a53fa0e8a28bc12556f087391","tid":1638034,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"依家啲post 主要集中係吹水台同時事台<br />\n而Post既種類繁多 睇到眼都花 <br />\n好多嘢都要禁落去先知 <br />\n有行動 有文宣 有討論 有攻略 <br />\n而琴日既遍地開花 <br />\n有資訊混亂同有人唔知道有活動既情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">當然係有休息撚</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而為左解決依個情況 唔洗下下search 慢慢搵<br />\n在此建議 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">所有行動同文宣 post 轉到活動台開</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">以下為行動台入面的標題</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n［緊急行動］ 今晚8點遍地開花<br />\n［行動］ 每日口罩日<br />\n［行動］10/10 tst 聲援811失眼義士<br />\n［外語文宣］馬蹄露紅豆沙一事<br />\n［文宣］點解我地要還手</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦知道好多人話tg可以幫到手 但基於難以整合 所以連登係依方面較好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">本身諗住召喚連仔幫手開個行動台 <br />\n但有個Ching留意到原來連登係有個台叫活動台 <br />\n個台係無咩人用 所以可以直接使用</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家都咁做 資訊一定更流通<br />\n<br />\n如果再有人唔知道每日嘅行動 <br />\n我就會打patpat <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同意請幫推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"078b2a9aebb410b8061a7d5d506c132b8b8ae9eb","tid":1638034,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1570d3a9b6b748db6400c46cd042c12b4f864f","tid":1638034,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3735fcc160b16066d3940b2271e497eed532dd","tid":1638034,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s